msgstr "image15"

msgid ""
"Click the *Other Node* button to create an :ref:`AudioStreamPlayer "
"<class_AudioStreamPlayer>` and rename it to ``MusicPlayer``."
msgstr ""
"Clique no botão *Other Node* para criar um :ref:`AudioStreamPlayer "
"<class_AudioStreamPlayer>` e renomei-o para ``MusicPlayer``."

